<c74object name="av.loadbang">

	<digest>
		Send a bang after the whole patcher is loaded
	</digest>

	<description>
		The av.loadbang is an alternative to the standard [loadbang] object. This loadbang is defered to the end of the patcher loading time, which allows to automatically load presets after the patch is initialized. In many cases a regular loadbang/loadmess is not sufficient, because the arguments/attributes loaded by the object are initialized after the patchers loadbang/loadmess objects.
	</description>

